quran[8]{c,v,t,f}:
  62,1,"Ohunkóhun tó wà nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ohunkóhun tó wà nínú ilẹ̀ ń ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ fún Allāhu, Ọba ẹ̀dá, Ẹni-Mímọ́ jùlọ, Alágbára, Ọlọ́gbọ́n.",""
  62,2,"Òun ni Ẹni tí Ó gbé Òjíṣẹ́ kan dìde láààrin àwọn aláìmọ̀ọ́nkọmọ̀ọ́nkà (àwọn aláìnítírà), tí ó ń ké àwọn āyah Rẹ̀ fún wọn. Ó ń fọ̀ wọ́n mọ́ (nínú ẹ̀ṣẹ̀). Ó sì ń kọ́ wọn ní Tírà àti ọgbọ́n ìjìnlẹ̀ (ìyẹn, sunnah), bí ó tilẹ̀ jẹ́ pé tẹ́lẹ̀tẹ́lẹ̀ wọ́n ti wà nínú ìṣìnà pọ́nńbélé.",""
  62,3,"(Iṣẹ́ jíjẹ́ rẹ̀ tún wà fún) àwọn mìíràn tí wọ́n máa wà nínú àwọn (ọmọlẹ́yìn rẹ̀), àmọ́ tí wọn kò ì pàdé wọn. (Allāhu) Òun ni Alágbára, Ọlọ́gbọ́n.",""
  62,4,"Ìyẹn ni oore àjùlọ Allāhu. Ó ń fún ẹni tí Ó bá fẹ́. Allāhu sì ni Olóore-àjùlọ ńlá.",""
  62,5,"Àpèjúwe ìjọ tí A la at-Taorāh bọ̀ lọ́rùn, lẹ́yìn náà tí wọn kò lò ó, ó dà bí àpèjúwe kẹ́tẹ́kẹ́tẹ́ tí ó ru ẹrù àwọn tírà ńlá ńlá. Aburú ni àpèjúwe àwọn tó pe àwọn āyah Allāhu ní irọ́. Allāhu kò sì níí fi ọ̀nà mọ ìjọ alábòsí.",""
  62,6,"Sọ pé: “Ẹ̀yin yẹhudi, tí ẹ bá lérò pé dájúdájú ẹ̀yin ni ọ̀rẹ́ Allāhu dípò àwọn ènìyàn (yòókù), ẹ tọrọ ikú nígbà náà tí ẹ bá jẹ́ olódodo.”",""
  62,7,"Wọn kò níí tọrọ rẹ̀ láéláé nítorí ohun tí ọwọ́ wọn ti tì ṣíwájú. Allāhu sì ni Onímọ̀ nípa àwọn alábòsí.",""
  62,8,"Sọ pé: “Dájúdájú ikú tí ẹ̀ ń sá fún, dájúdájú ó máa pàdé yín. Lẹ́yìn náà, wọn yóò da yín padà sí ọ̀dọ̀ Onímọ̀-ìkọ̀kọ̀ àti gban̄gba. Ó sì máa fún yín ní ìró ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́.”",""
